{"tid":2229167,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"法院暫緩微信禁令 美司法部上訴","createTime":"2020-10-04T07:50:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-04T08:00:55.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"cf7100ed0296d708fbbf42d5c5e67bfaf15d535a","tid":2229167,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T07:50:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20201004/UPZCN6ZWAZGDXNWAXIKAAYOJEM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20201004%2FUPZCN6ZWAZGDXNWAXIKAAYOJEM%2F&d=eUEb8trTAlhqW9E3j8wil%2FZItop%2BIuorIKtd308SUMA%3D&h=61fe6be2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20201004%2FUPZCN6ZWAZGDXNWAXIKAAYOJEM%2F&h=80eab1f1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20201004/UPZCN6ZWAZGDXNWAXIKAAYOJEM/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n法院暫緩微信禁令 美司法部上訴<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/RQ1H7L0ko364AToKyTMqZZlTQeE=/1222x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/K4FYEOMH75HUVGBOBR6JATSCPM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FRQ1H7L0ko364AToKyTMqZZlTQeE%3D%2F1222x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FK4FYEOMH75HUVGBOBR6JATSCPM.jpg&h=2dadca19&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■美國商務部尋求法院同意禁止下載WeChat。 資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n美國特朗普政府針對中國通訊應用程式微信（WeChat）的禁令，被法院頒下臨時禁制令暫無法執行後，周五（2日）就此提出上訴。上訴方司法部稱，繼續允許微信「不受約束的使用」將對國家安全和外交政策構成威脅。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：美重啟冷戰政策 禁共產黨員申綠卡  羅冠聰：劍指中共<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n強調微信威脅國安<br />\n<br />\n美國政府原定在9月20日起禁止蘋果和Alphabet旗下的Google在國內的應用程式平台提供微信的下載和更新，同時禁止美國與微信進行其他交易。一批華裔用戶認為禁令將損害他們的通訊自由，以禁令或違反憲法有關保障言論自由的第一修正案為由，入稟法院試圖推翻行政命令。司法部周五表示，已就加州法院地方法官比勒（Laurel Beeler）在9月19日頒下的臨時禁制令，向巡迴上訴法院提出上訴。騰訊的美國發言人暫未回應。<br />\n<br />\n入稟挑戰行政命令的「美國微信用戶聯盟」，。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n除了微信外，美國商務部原定9月27日起亦實施針對中國短片分享平台TikTok的行政命令，。。。。。。。。。。，亦頒下了臨時禁制令暫時阻止華府執行有關禁令。<br />\n<br />\n路透社"},{"pid":"2fe4a561b39ebde4d9156db1f6caabdff8d21c05","tid":2229167,"uid":270889,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T07:51:47.000Z","msg":"好撚on9 <br />\n淨係wechat pay完全避過US$ <br />\n已經一早要禁啦"},{"pid":"95e6789184f4d98f943f2d494b99a75fd95efc8e","tid":2229167,"uid":334720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2fe4a561b39ebde4d9156db1f6caabdff8d21c05","tid":2229167,"uid":270889,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T07:51:47.000Z","msg":"好撚on9 <br />\n淨係wechat pay完全避過US$ <br />\n已經一早要禁啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T07:57:47.000Z","msg":"details ?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 即係點"},{"pid":"2ad94e209f53bb368f4d774961b10561bb9c38b8","tid":2229167,"uid":270889,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"95e6789184f4d98f943f2d494b99a75fd95efc8e","tid":2229167,"uid":334720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2fe4a561b39ebde4d9156db1f6caabdff8d21c05","tid":2229167,"uid":270889,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T07:51:47.000Z","msg":"好撚on9 <br />\n淨係wechat pay完全避過US$ <br />\n已經一早要禁啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T07:57:47.000Z","msg":"details ?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 即係點"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T08:00:55.000Z","msg":"如果全世界都收wechat pay<br />\n(已經好多地方收)<br />\n咁支畜咪一機通行 連外幣都唔洗用<br />\n好似係"}]}